其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/H%E1%BB%93i-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-Nh%E1%BB%8B-h%C3%A0-nh%E1%BA%ADt-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%A1c/poem-qnQB5ulUE1YlLtVdK4m1LA">Hồi tưởng độ Nhị hà nhật, nhân tác - 迴想渡珥河日因作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%93ng/Ng%C5%A9-y-ca/poem-rEDZQ8MAXgC3CakbxwIKnA">Ngũ y ca - 五噫歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-gCZu3ihGAmC2ewleau-d9Q">Lương Hồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Qu%C3%A2n-minh-th%E1%BA%A7n-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-4LZLPygbzJT_4XFSxX-FAQ">Quân minh thần lương - 君明臣良</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Tr%E1%BA%A5n-Nam-Quan/poem--cwIimn8ufdouXrN49NYRg">Trấn Nam Quan - 鎮南關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
